<p style="text-align:justify">Drosero Cafe & Restro is cafe cum lounge by Ghaus Enterprise. Our story begin when my thirst for
    very peppy Italian cuisine with fine aromatic Mediterranean herbs as Rosemary, Basil, Thyme and
    Presley. Another cuisine that made my mouth water was during my stay in Gulf countries, their food
    introduce me to heavily Mediterranean taste, the juicy kebabs and healthy hummus breakfast. The earthy
    smell of freshly ground coffee beans, the real Espresso shots and mind blowing Americano was raising my
    thirst higher for something different. Another of my passion in thoughtful and never ending reading was
    missing in our neighbourhood. So here we present to you authentic handmade food and drinks in the in rustic
    and calming ambience in Drosero Cafe & Restro.</p>



